<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, August 5 (Xinhua) -- Tunis stock exchange index closed
at 453.12 points Wednesday, up 0.05 percent against Tuesday's
closing.
</P>
<P>
The stock exchange daily release said Wednesday that 35,229
shares worth 1,122,074 dinars (nearly 1 million U.S. dollars) were
traded in 197 transactions compared to 76,604 shares at 2 million
dinars (1.7 million dollars) in 211 transactions Tuesday. 
</P>
