<HEADLINE> Macao SAR Preparatory Committee Work Group Ends Meeting </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZHUHAI, August 6 (Xinhua) -- The Economic and Legal Affairs
Work Group for the Preparatory Committee of the Macao Special
Administrative Region (SAR) under the National People's Congress
ended its third meeting here today.
</P>
<P>
Participants attending the two-day meeting discussed pension
security for the region's government officials and the region's
financial affairs.
</P>
<P>
Members of Legal Group continued discussions on Macao's 135
existing laws, and agreed that most do not contravene the basic
law of the Macao SAR.  
