<P>
Guangzhou: min. 28 degrees C., max. 34 degrees C., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 26 degrees C., max. 31 degrees C., thunder
showers, calm to gentle breeze. 
</P>
