million Singapore dollars in cash will be returned to SPH
shareholders, amounting to 1.22 Singapore dollars for every share,
and 40,644,370 shares will be canceled under the capital
Reduction.
</P>
<P>
A SPH press release said that the SPH management is constantly
striving to improve the return equity of the Group, thereby
increasing Shareholders' value. 
