<HEADLINE> International Club for Overseas Investors in Northeast China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHENYANG, August 6 (Xinhua) --An international club for
overseas investors was announced to start business Monday in
Shenyang, capital of northeast China's Liaoning Province.
</P>
<P>
The 10,000-square-meter club was built inside the Shenyang
High-Tech Industrial Development Zone at a cost of 170 million
yuan.
</P>
<P>
