China and the only international club approved by the Shenyang
City government.
</P>
<P>
The club has made arrangements with major hotels in other
large Chinese cities for international investors to make
reservations at the Shenyang club, according to local sources.
</P>
<P>
Liaoning Province, one of China's old industrial centers, had
had 16,473 overseas-funded firms by the end of last year.
</P>
<P>
The city also has become an economic hub for northeast China,
and many international organizations have representative offices
in the city. 
