the deterioration of the humanitarian situation in the country
and condemned the violent actions against the humanitarian workers
in the country.
</P>
<P>
The Council expressed its support for the efforts to create
conditions for the provision and distribution of the
humanitarian assistance by the United Nations and its agencies
as well as the non-governmental organizations.  
